    <item>
      <title>I’m so happy to announce my next album ‘Of The Earth’ will be released on March ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DTfRgEViGGk/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/616130758_18556769647059940_5545015628031096749_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgwOTg0MDc2MjQ5ODYwNTM0NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwNjd4MTQyMi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=9g55WJTQUGoQ7kNvwGFwLo7&amp;_nc_oc=AdpGQrkeWZHE89_rFUYJKR5htlTczLmH4TvBcs1aZk36sA3bYoxq2tcQ3CScekzbWcE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=GKct29fYZJrKuCAaUABixw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzeH3LwRBCSYyCtcjds7eYKCNABClrpjzxJc2HmA0g9mw&amp;oe=69C9943B" alt="Instagram billede fra @shabakahutchings" /></p><p><strong>@shabakahutchings</strong></p><p>I’m so happy to announce my next album ‘Of The Earth’ will be released on March 6th. <br/>
<br/>
Produced, performed and mixed by myself, ‘creative mastering’ by @_ja__min <br/>
<br/>
None of the music was started with the intention of being part of an album. It’s been this freewheeling process of researching equipment and seeing what music is suggested to me once manuals have been read and YouTube tutorial videos have been watched multiple times. It’s been about trusting my ears, being ok with not ‘knowing’ what I’m doing, knowing what I like, trusting my taste, not allowing the impulse to self deprecate stop me from keeping on playfully experimenting, and being open to hearing when something of worth comes up. <br/>
<br/>
The record comes out on my newly formed imprint Shabaka Records. In today’s climate, independence is power.<br/>
<br/>
The first two singles ‘A Future Untold’ and ‘Marwa The Mountain’ are out today. <br/>
<br/>
Each song on the album is represented by an artwork that I’ve worked on alongside the music, and which I see as visual representations of the sound.<br/>
<br/>
Link in bio to listen and Pre-Order.<br/>
<br/>
Slide 1: @atibaphoto <br/>
Slide 2 &amp; 3: @josephouechen <br/>
Slide 5 &amp; 6: #marwabelghazi <br/>
Slide 4 &amp; 7: Original artwork by me</p>]]></description>
